OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1784744311
OL,3,CTributes paid to former Newcastle
OL,4,CUnited player and manager Kevin Keegan
OL,6,FOur Sports Correspondent Simon O'
OL,7,FRourke looks back on the life of
OL,8,Flegendary footballer and manager Kevin
OL,9,FKeegan.
OL,11,FTributes have been paid to the former
OL,12,FNewcastle United footballer and
OL,13,Fmanager, Kevin Keegan, who has died at
OL,14,Fthe age of 75.
OL,16,FIn a statement, his family said: "It
OL,17,Fis with immense sadness that we
OL,18,Fannounce that Kevin Keegan has passed
OL,19,Faway at the age of 75.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G1/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
