PN,39502
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1784744311
OL,3,CTributes paid to former Newcastle
OL,4,CUnited player and manager Kevin Keegan
OL,6,FKeegan, who also played for and
OL,7,Fmanaged the England national team, had
OL,8,Fbeen battling cancer and was
OL,9,Fsurrounded by his wife and daughters
OL,10,Fin his final moments.
OL,12,FThe family statement continued:
OL,13,F"Kevin, a double Ballon D'or winner,
OL,14,Fwas a much loved husband, father and
OL,15,Fgrandfather. The family would like to
OL,16,Fthank Kevin's incredible medical team
OL,17,Ffor all their support.
OL,19,F"This is a hugely difficult time and
OL,20,Fthey are requesting space and privacy."
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G2/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
