OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1784744311
OL,3,CTributes paid to former Newcastle
OL,4,CUnited player and manager Kevin Keegan
OL,6,FThe Newcastle United legend revealed
OL,7,Fhe had cancer in January 2026, which
OL,8,Flater spread to stage four.
OL,10,FIn 1992, Keegan made his first step
OL,11,Finto management at Newcastle, leading
OL,12,Fthem into the Premier League and to
OL,13,Fwithin touching distance of the 1995-
OL,14,F96 title, but they missed out to
OL,15,FManchester United.
OL,17,FA statement from Newcastle United
OL,18,Fcalled Keegan "the beating heart of
OL,19,Fthe club for generations of
OL,20,Fsupporters".
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G3/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
