PN,39507
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1784744311
OL,3,CTributes paid to former Newcastle
OL,4,CUnited player and manager Kevin Keegan
OL,6,F"Today, we mourn the loss of a true
OL,7,Fgiant of our history, and at the
OL,8,Fappropriate moment, we will carefully
OL,9,Fconsider how we shape a lasting
OL,10,Ftribute to Kevin's remarkable life and
OL,11,Flegacy.
OL,13,F"Rest in peace, King Kev."
OL,15,FFans are gathering outside St James'
OL,16,FPark to pay their tributes to former
OL,17,FNewcastle and England manager Kevin
OL,18,FKeegan.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G7/11
