OL,3,CTributes paid to former Newcastle
OL,4,CUnited player and manager Kevin Keegan
OL,6,FAlan Shearer paid tribute to his hero
OL,7,Fand friend Kevin Keegan following the
OL,8,Fdeath of his former Newcastle manager
OL,9,Fat the age of 75.
OL,11,FKeegan was in charge at St James' Park
OL,12,Fwhen the club paid a then world-record
OL,13,Ffee of #15million to sign Shearer in
OL,14,F1996.
OL,16,F"My Hero. My manager. My friend. Sleep
OL,17,Feasy Boss," Shearer wrote on X.
OL,26,@xD@AOUyD@KO]
