PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1784744311
OL,3,CTributes paid to former Newcastle
OL,4,CUnited player and manager Kevin Keegan
OL,6,FAfter leaving St James' Park in
OL,7,FJanuary 1997, a brief stint at Fulham
OL,8,Ffollowed before he became England
OL,9,Fmanager in 1999 following Glenn
OL,10,FHoddle's departure.
OL,12,FAfter overseeing a disappointing Euro
OL,13,F2000 campaign, Keegan resigned on the
OL,14,Fback of defeat by Germany at Wembley,
OL,15,Fthe last match at the national stadium
OL,16,Fbefore it was rebuilt.
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}        G9/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
