PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1784744311
OL,3,CTributes paid to former Newcastle
OL,4,CUnited player and manager Kevin Keegan
OL,6,FA spell at Manchester City followed
OL,7,Fand then an emotional return to
OL,8,FNewcastle in 2008, but he only lasted
OL,9,Feight months at St James' Park
OL,10,Ffollowing tensions with the board and
OL,11,Fowner Mike Ashley.
OL,13,FOn the international stage, he scored
OL,14,F21 goals in 63 England appearances and
OL,15,Fplayed at the 1982 World Cup finals.
OL,17,FNorth East Mayor Kim McGuinness said:
OL,1,W~k4~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}       G10/11
OL,2,W/*%+, "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,,,
