PN,39511
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F395A1784744311
OL,3,CTributes paid to former Newcastle
OL,4,CUnited player and manager Kevin Keegan
OL,6,F"Kevin Keegan brought joy to so many
OL,7,Fof us in the North East and across the
OL,8,Fworld. It is hard to believe someone
OL,9,Fwith so much energy and passion is no
OL,10,Flonger with us.
OL,12,F"King Kev fought such a brave battle
OL,13,Fagainst cancer, and while today we
OL,14,Fwill all mourn his passing, we should
OL,15,Falso find room to celebrate with a
OL,16,Fsmile everything he achieved."
